      "seed": 449997161,
      "version": 362,
      "versionNonce": 625188580,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776987582747,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "第 1 跳：\ni = curEnd = 0, fasthest = 2\n从 i 扫过的下标（0）起跳，最远跳到 2",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "第 1 跳：\ni = curEnd = 0, fasthest = 2\n从 i 扫过的下标（0）起跳，最远跳到 2",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "89NGkjyFy-3awXtmiTqJY",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 20.200266287364684,
      "y": 609.1927729397839,
      "width": 322.1439208984375,
      "height": 60,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#f08c00",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "ad",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1030968393,
      "version": 396,
      "versionNonce": 1601480412,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776987599345,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "第 2 跳：\ni = curEnd = 2, fasthest = 4\n从 i 扫过的下标（0, 1, 2）起跳，最远跳到 4",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "第 2 跳：\ni = curEnd = 2, fasthest = 4\n从 i 扫过的下标（0, 1, 2）起跳，最远跳到 4",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "MbgvejiwFzzRq8I6iJzDy",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -23.099426006279828,
      "y": 704.3514397055937,
      "width": 411.9359436035156,
      "height": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#f08c00",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "ae",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1987306281,
      "version": 907,
      "versionNonce": 1550522249,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776987481913,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "注意：curEnd 记录的是每次跳跃时能达到的最远距离，\n不表示下次跳跃的起点坐标。\n\n下次跳跃的起点坐标：小于等于 curEnd，即 i 扫过的所有\n起跳点中跳最远的点，最远距离始终由 fasthest 记录。",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "注意：curEnd 记录的是每次跳跃时能达到的最远距离，\n不表示下次跳跃的起点坐标。\n\n下次跳跃的起点坐标：小于等于 curEnd，即 i 扫过的所有\n起跳点中跳最远的点，最远距离始终由 fasthest 记录。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
